  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pot on medium heat and sauté the diced onion until translucent.",
    "Add the sliced carrot and celery, cook for 5 minutes until they soften slightly.",
    "Stir in the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the tomato paste, mixed herbs, and dashi extract, stirring to combine.",
    "Pour in the vegetable broth and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Add the rinsed lentils, reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 25 minutes.",
    "Stir occasionally, adding more broth if the stew becomes too thick.",
    "Season with salt and pepper, then ladle into a wooden board and garnish with chopped parsley before serving."
  ],
